text: Anders Poulsen (born 4 June 1981) is a Danish football referee. He has refereed in the Danish Superliga, in UEFA Europa League qualifying games and at international games at under-17 level. ==References== == External links == * * * * Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Danish football referees Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
